@Backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5265

### Get all shows
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/shows
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all characters
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/characters
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single character (BUG: returns 500 if id not found)
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/characters/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a character (BUG: returns 200 instead of 201)
POST {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/characters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Walter White",
  "actorName": "Bryan Cranston",
  "bio": "A high school chemistry teacher turned methamphetamine producer.",
  "isMainCharacter": true,
  "status": "Deceased",
  "showId": 1
}

###

### Get all episodes
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/episodes
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all quotes
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/api/quotes
Accept: application/json

###

### OpenAPI spec (only available in Development)
GET {{Backend_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###
